page.title: 11HOUSING
page.content:
Here is a list of buildings of special architectural or historic interest in Rostrevor.
"Fairy Hill", Church Street. "Forestbrook", 11 Forestbrook Road. "Riverside", 38 Bridge Street. "Brookvale", 37 Water Street. "Glynn-na-Shee", 33 Water Street. "The Willows", Horner's Lane. "Old Hall", Warrenpoint Road. "Trevor Lodge", Warrenpoint Road. "Arno's Vale", Drumsesk. "Rostrevor House", Greenpark Road. "Carpenham", Greenpark Road. "Greenpark", Ballymoney TL. "Benvenu", Kilbroney Road. 28,30,32 & 34 Water Street. (Alms Houses).
